{"tid":144604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣戰！南亞狗見本地人就打","createTime":"2017-03-05T14:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T14:04:39.000Z","uid":66246,"like":33,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c0c4dfad5ad04dad392cc5e6664dde43825e65","tid":144604,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170305/bkn-20170305184321901-0305_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170305%2Fbkn-20170305184321901-0305_00822_001.html&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ510Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0c9c35f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170305/bkn-20170305184321901-0305_00822_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南亞人肆虐元朗，有傳其中一幫人更見本地人就打。近日網上便流傳一片段，一名本地男子疑「無辜辜」當街被人一拳打到瞓低。據片段所見，本月1日凌晨2時57分，一名穿深色西裝的男子在元朗路邊與一名男友人談天，未幾，3男1女南亞裔人士從轉角位走出，其中2男女走在前方，另2人則跟在後方，3名男子均身形魁梧。當他們在西裝男身旁走過時，其中一名走在後方、一邊行一邊用右手拿着手機傾電話的戴帽白衣南亞漢，突然揮左鈎拳重擊西裝男的右邊臉，西裝男猝不及防，應聲倒地。白衫南亞漢之後若無其事，施施然離開，其同行2名南亞男女則稍為加快步伐，走最後的南亞漢一度轉身雙手作「耍冧」狀，之後亦逃去。 <br />\n<br />\n原本坐在路邊的本地男子睹狀，即時衝前喝止，並想阻止他們離開，惟不成功，於是尾隨他們走去，而後方有一名男途人亦加入追截。被打的西裝男其後自行爬起，坐在路旁，神色痛苦，未能自行站起。至2分鐘後，多名途人路經，即時上前慰問，並合力將西裝男扶起，搬來一張櫈讓他坐下休息。"},{"pid":"017959bc0d7a808dbae371e2b15b5ae9f789e3ea","tid":144604,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"咁我地識做喇"},{"pid":"74a9c853e78743a44676bec966a21aab385ce385","tid":144604,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"差佬見到蝻都縮埋啦"},{"pid":"1fcbf91076d726b568775f2e2342230a6b0a8b82","tid":144604,"uid":50764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"又唔係個個南亞人都係咁既。。<br />\n你向邊個宣戰先"},{"pid":"9970a7930551f3f33202208489a3d276e9246d3b","tid":144604,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤，本地人打人先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee45bc0e3e9aba6bd6acd05e9c99d57086ce6b0","tid":144604,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔繼續鍵盤反南<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963a3201400e5387a92c96b75cdb29dea8c097d4","tid":144604,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"南亞支那本是一家"},{"pid":"d9d6be4c3463a31c81eb2d978c179cbed6890720","tid":144604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77a6b55e5a218739f5b1ee1233f5ab6c0a0a863","tid":144604,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"樓主玩分化 一定係鬼"},{"pid":"70ec91de52b38fae15f98027a41d8b25b976b97d","tid":144604,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"低等人種"},{"pid":"629f666e6fdc59cc3eca03daa2771a8e5a2a3770","tid":144604,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主玩分化 一定係鬼</blockquote><br />\n邊個打邊個就係鬼"},{"pid":"128e8fbf7238d97bf7278fa23d965574e2a63424","tid":144604,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"ba6138936b52c0b50cef27f903a5685c1e44f3f4","tid":144604,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"吹牙 禾地南亞狗大撚哂架喎"},{"pid":"9ee9e234e8e6c29d82faa323f544308f1faea181","tid":144604,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:19:53.000Z","msg":"Ust南亞狗又要出黎消毒"},{"pid":"cc53984eb5f8b16a0c745f19c47bebdea542cfb0","tid":144604,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05